==Description==

The '''TechDraw ExtensionExtendLine''' tool extends a cosmetic line or centerline at both ends.

[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionExtendLineExample.png|300px]]
{{Caption|On the right a centerline extended at both ends}}

==Usage==

# Optionally specify the delta distance with the [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionSelectLineAttributes|TechDraw ExtensionSelectLineAttributes]] tool.
# Select a single cosmetic line or centerline.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionExtendLine.svg|16px]] [[TechDraw_ExtensionExtendLine|Extend Line]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|TechDraw → Extensions: Attributes/Modifications → [[Image:TechDraw_ExtensionExtendLine.svg|16px]] Extend Line}} option from the menu.
# The line is extended at both ends.


